{"tid":473962,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[Ryzen]新手想更新電腦硬件求意見","createTime":"2017-11-19T16:59:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-20T16:26:48.000Z","uid":28013,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"52aebb0cc61c27569c183f4eb09c4f03b115acba","tid":473962,"uid":28013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T16:59:11.000Z","msg":"如題，小弟3~5年前係悠二list到執左條砌機list ~3500<br />\n而家想upgrade 下零件 主要想再戰3~4年<br />\n要求唔高 但求順玩gta 5 / pubg(普通畫質就夠)<br />\n大約年尾到出年年頭會換<br />\n筆直約3500 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現spec :  <br />\n板:ASrock fm2a88mhd<br />\nU: AMD A8 5600k<br />\nram: ddr3 8gbx1<br />\n顯卡: 1050Ti<br />\nAC: antec 550w<br />\n<br />\n由於之前換過AC同顯卡所以呢兩樣比較新, 更新零件亦唔會考慮呢兩樣住<br />\n上網做左陣功課, 睇過d零件之後, 目前想換<br />\n<br />\n板:MSI/ ASUS B350大板($780 / $820)<br />\nU: R5 1600/ 1600x ($1650 / $1900)<br />\nRAM: Corsair CMV8GX4M1A2133C15 8GB DDR4 2144mhz ($550)<br />\n再換個機箱<br />\n總數約$2980+機箱~$3270+機箱<br />\n<br />\n求意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問幾個問題:<br />\n1.筆直內(3500) 想玩GAME順係咪換呢三樣最有效率?<br />\n2. msi 同asus 塊板邊塊比較好?<br />\n3. 我AMD A8 冇超頻(新手唔識玩), 如果之後換R5 唔超頻其實係咪唔洗換1600x? <br />\n4. 或者我咁問, 1600/1600x除左ghz既分別其實有咩唔同?<br />\n5. ram 呢條好唔好? 我上網搵左陣覺得呢條比較就價, 如果唔用呢條有無比較好既alternative?<br />\n6. 可唔可以將我舊個條ddr3 ram 同新買既ddr4 ram 一齊插? 定係我買兩條ddr4 ram比較好?<br />\n7. 而家用緊半TB既機械硬碟, 仲有120gb 剩, 考慮遊戲效能定係我應該分少少筆直去換ssd?如果作用不大就唔換硬碟<br />\n8.如有再補充, 感謝解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b4206feae8af5c4e7329761f4134919e2e11250","tid":473962,"uid":30510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T17:01:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">顯</span></span>"},{"pid":"b2dfbf9021109d08408eebc126b294da595ea947","tid":473962,"uid":28013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T17:05:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">顯</span></span></blockquote><br />\n巴打可唔可以講多D?"},{"pid":"9d3aaa070d0440bb6161ff322f2eb4cbc58921d2","tid":473962,"uid":28013,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T17:06:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">顯</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 岩岩睇完其他POST 對唔住 我以後會叫返display card"},{"pid":"521e0513c0b1f14b2e5097cd5cd67ca24f7a6afd","tid":473962,"uid":35403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T17:06:58.000Z","msg":"顯你老母卡"},{"pid":"23ff892fb9cfb795f51ae4263c54f633a6996dcc","tid":473962,"uid":28013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T17:14:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>顯你老母卡</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新手 SORRY"},{"pid":"129a4f836caf9bc3cfe331b59015c0e91cc08132","tid":473962,"uid":22817,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T17:15:52.000Z","msg":"得3500 你目前可以留既有顯示卡 火牛 hdd, ryzen 同corsair ram就算更新左bios 都比較多人反映唔夾ram"},{"pid":"dcf9b4bad5597766ade2338f08459170f30cb06f","tid":473962,"uid":37210,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T17:18:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/011839_4a7a9004c068615d2de5c30d0da635b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F011839_4a7a9004c068615d2de5c30d0da635b5.jpg&h=41c2dac6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我自己個Spec"},{"pid":"ec8457a81e9de60275bf9b6c99dbede71311c1a1","tid":473962,"uid":37210,"like":0,